# Task Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create task (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Build a CRUD API",
  "description": "Create users CRUD with NestJS",
  "internId": "<intern-id>",
  "mentorId": "<mentor-id>",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-01T10:00:00Z"
}

### Get all tasks (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get task by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/tasks/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update task status (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/tasks/{{id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Update task details (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/tasks/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

### Add task comment (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/tasks/{{id}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "content": "This is a new comment."
}

### Delete task (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/tasks/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
